,"msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0292a7f5465a66dc07b0df2bec8b64479f02c89","tid":1483234,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">突發<br />\n西環要雨<br />\n大家集氣 淋濕班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2bfa9198e4cedd53d9b65d1e6393c1634cde9d4d","tid":1483234,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:18:36.000Z","msg":"突發！西環有狗查市民，大家小心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGgAMP9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGgAMP9.png&h=afe7f428&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"910882baebe0a7245c083c0a4d86ec1a488d920b","tid":1483234,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"幫手推俾現場睇呀！"},{"pid":"857d5ddbca705511f7e84db7bc979ac6de02fab2","tid":1483234,"uid":200957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"SoGO門口附近果幾條路其實塞左好多個鐘!<br />\n銅鑼灣地鐵站既人目前係入唔到去  又出唔到黎<br />\n如果未入維園既求大家唔好擔遮<br />\n左穿右插就可以殺出條路去維園<br />\n<br />\n我由四點係銅鑼灣sogo到維園果條路塞左三個鐘 <br />\n依家關遮殺出一條血路先可以到到維園<br />\n但結果維園原來好少人<br />\n個個塞哂係地鐵站附近<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好行去皇室堡 sogo個方向 <br />\n呢條街係對流緊<br />\n因為有好多人未去維園架<br />\n<br />\n維園目前其實好少人!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好怕淋雨  因為塞左咁耐  都因為個個都開遮"},{"pid":"8cdf926a2e5ba37a32703513c13637d0a7d44271","tid":1483234,"uid":10778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7c16dc97d0c735e6fef60586f37fbd3b1a66e2","tid":1483234,"uid":89011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"外國勢力要我地和理非 就和理非<br />\n黑社會、大陸哩想放燃燒彈 就屌撚柒佢<br />\n中共想入解放軍 就返去訓覺"},{"pid":"209105e3ccfc4a2199b15f343e274b8a05f4ba55","tid":1483234,"uid